Here's what this demo does and why it makes the point effectively:

---

### 🔑 Key Features

| Feature | Details |
|---|---|
| **3 Algorithms** | Bubble Sort, Merge Sort, Quick Sort running simultaneously |
| **Live counters** | Comparisons and swaps/writes update in real time |
| **Color coding** | Active bars (white), pivot (orange), sorted (yellow-green), merging (pink) |
| **Winner badge** | After sorting, the algorithm with fewest comparisons is crowned 🏆 |
