| **Speed control** | Slow down to watch the logic, speed up to see the final counts |
| **Complexity table** | Full Big-O reference with color-coded good/bad ratings |

### 📌 How to use it to convince your colleague
1. Set array size to **100+** and hit **Start Sort**
2. Watch Bubble Sort still churning while the others finish
3. Compare the **comparison counters** — Bubble Sort will show **~5,000–10,000** vs **~600–700** for the others
4. Point to the complexity table and the verdict paragraph at the bottom

