<h1>🔢 Sorting Algorithm Showdown</h1>
<p class="subtitle">Why Bubble Sort is <em>not</em> always the best choice — visualized live</p>

<div class="controls">
  <label>Array size:
    <select id="sizeSelect">
      <option value="20">20</option>
