        <td class="good">O(log n)</td>
        <td class="bad">No</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <p style="margin-top:10px; font-size:0.78rem; color:#777;">
    * Quick Sort worst case occurs with poor pivot selection (e.g., already-sorted arrays). Randomized pivot selection largely avoids this.
  </p>
